Malaysia Plans New Lending Guidelines for Financial Institutions

-- B y   C h o n g   P o o i   K o o n
-- 
2011-03-23T10:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/malaysia-plans-new-lending-guidelines-for-financial-institutions.html
Malaysia will introduce new lending
guidelines for financial institutions in the third quarter of
this year, central bank Governor Zeti Akhtar Aziz told reporters
in  Kuala Lumpur  today. This is to ensure “responsible” lending
practices, she said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chong Pooi Koon in Kuala Lumpur at 
 pchong17@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Barry Porter in Kuala Lumpur at 
 bporter10@bloomberg.net  